{"tid":2283911,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中共剝奪民主 加拿大擬讓港青更易在當地工作！！！","createTime":"2020-11-13T02:34:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-13T03:05:48.000Z","uid":199670,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"da7018ef39cf5521abfe8b2db49c0ff8660fd64d","tid":2283911,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:34:07.000Z","msg":"香港立法會4名議員被取消資格，美國國務卿蓬佩奧形容，中國共產黨利用扭曲的愛國主義，剝奪自由及民主的要求，推動這些行動及政策的人士將須負上責任。 <br />\n<br />\n另外，加拿大移民部長門迪奇諾透露，香港年青人可更容易到當地讀書及工作，過去三年在加拿大大學畢業的學生，可以提出在當地申請工作，最多三年，並提供更便捷的途徑，以便取得永久居留。<br />\n<br />\n門迪奇諾又表示，會加快他們的配偶及子女到加拿大的程序。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">又多個選擇了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%93%AC%E4%BD%A9%E5%A5%A7%E6%8C%87%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E5%89%9D%E5%A5%AA%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB-%E5%8A%A0%E6%8B%BF%E5%A4%A7%E6%93%AC%E8%AE%93%E6%B8%AF%E9%9D%92%E6%9B%B4%E6%98%93%E5%9C%A8%E7%95%B6%E5%9C%B0%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C-222913682.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E8%2593%25AC%25E4%25BD%25A9%25E5%25A5%25A7%25E6%258C%2587%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25B1%25E5%2589%259D%25E5%25A5%25AA%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB-%25E5%258A%25A0%25E6%258B%25BF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2593%25AC%25E8%25AE%2593%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%259D%2592%25E6%259B%25B4%25E6%2598%2593%25E5%259C%25A8%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BD%259C-222913682.html&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2Byo5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=83e70201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%93%AC%E4%BD%A9%E5%A5%A7%E6%8C%87%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E5%89%9D%E5%A5%AA%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB-%E5%8A%A0%E6%8B%BF%E5%A4%A7%E6%93%AC%E8%AE%93%E6%B8%AF%E9%9D%92%E6%9B%B4%E6%98%93%E5%9C%A8%E7%95%B6%E5%9C%B0%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C-222913682.html</a>"},{"pid":"f5d2c4fdc2ee169506dad0bc28cc7c60e011d226","tid":2283911,"uid":205043,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:35:12.000Z","msg":"會員 傷子情歌 #199670 疑為狗